khush_jammu.title: Technical Evangelist
khush_jammu.bio: Angular Google Developer Expert. I am a Computer Science Engineer specialised in Web. International speaker and trainer. I am an Angular fanboy and a community activist fighting for the JavaScript revolution. I have lived and worked for all sorts of companies in Germany, Brazil, UK and Spain. I am always up for a good challenge. I enjoy running AngularLabs London, mentoring students, participating in the community, giving talks and writing technical articles at Medium.
